    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that looks and drives like new.",
