    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an unrivaled opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine condition. This specimen has been meticulously curated and maintained to the highest standards, offering a showroom-fresh experience that defies its year. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, every detail reflects a commitment to excellence. This is more than just a car; it is an investment in quality for the driver who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
